<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12113m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12113m">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12113m"> 113(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ contradict 50 &mdash; ~</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> il subira cinquante coups ou gardera le silence pendant un temps d&eacute;termin&eacute;. M&ecirc;me punition s&apos;il a contredit l&apos;un de ses fr&egrave;res ou cherch&eacute; &agrave; s&apos;excuser devant une r&eacute;primande qu&apos;on lui faisait. <br><font color="green">[&hellip; he will suffer fifty blows or will keep silent for a set time. The same punishment holds if he contradicts one of his brethren or tries to evade a reprimand he is due.]</font> <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 56</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
